---
name: playwright
version: 1.0.0
description: |
  Browser automation and testing using Playwright CLI and scripts. Replaces
  the @playwright/mcp MCP server with direct npx playwright commands and
  temporary script files.
allowed-tools:
  - Bash
  - Read
  - Write
